title: Flight Simulator 2020 - World Update V - Stockholm
description:
In this video we will fly to Stockholm and have a look at all POI's which have been added as part of World Update V to MSFS 2020. Stockholm has several POI's which are looking really nice so if you like nice palaces and arena's it is definitely a good idea to fly over Stockholm yourself.
